            <abstract>
                <p>Cycle of magic prayers of the masṭǝma-ʾagānǝnt-type (drowner of demons) for the entire week beginning with the prayer for
                    Monday, each of which using ʾasmāt and referring to one of the archangels as protector.</p>
            </abstract>
