    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="bibliography">
                <listRelation>
                    <relation name="saws:isDifferentTo" active="LIT7867MastemaYan" passive="LIT7868MastemaYas"/>
                    <relation name="saws:isDifferentTo" active="LIT7867MastemaYan" passive="LIT7869MasteLayal"/>
                    <relation name="saws:isDifferentTo" active="LIT7867MastemaYan" passive="LIT7867MastemaYan"/>
                </listRelation>
            </div>
            <div type="edition">
                <note>The following text is taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="EMIPms00537"/>, where a prayer for Saturday is missing and two
                    prayers for Sunday (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ʿǝlata qadāmit</foreign> and <foreign xml:lang="gez">ʿǝlata ʾǝḫud</foreign>) 
                    are present.</note>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="Monday">
                    <note>Referring to <persName ref="PRS7049Michael"/> as protector.</note>
                    <ab>
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቀዲስ፡ ፩አምላክ፡ ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መስጥመ፡ አጋንንት፡ ዘዕለተ፡ ሰኑይ፡ አቃቢሁ፡ ሚካኤል፡ መልአክ፡ ኮከቡኒ፡ ቀመር፡ 
                        <gap reason="ellipsis"/>
                    </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="Tuesday">
                    <note>Referring to <persName ref="PRS4377Gabriel"/> as protector.</note>
                    <ab>
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩አምላክ፡ ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መስጥመ፡ አጋንንት፡ ዘዕለተ፡ <del rend="overUnderlined">ረቡአ፡</del> ሰሉስ፡ 
                        አቃቢሁ፡ ገብርኤል፡ መልአክ፡ ኮከቡኒ፡ አልሰግሮን፡ ጋኔኑ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/>
                    </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="Wednesday">
                    <note>Referring to <persName ref="PRS9684Uriel"/> as protector.</note>
                    <ab>
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩አምላክ፡ ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መስጥመ፡ አጋንንት፡ ዘዕለተ፡ <sic>ረበዕ፡</sic> አቃቢሁ፡ ኡራኤል፡ መልአክ፡ ኮከቡኒ፡ አግርርጅ፡ ጋኔኑ፡
                        <gap reason="ellipsis"/>
                    </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="Thursday">
                    <note>Referring to <persName ref="PRS8083Raphael"/> as protector.</note>
                    <ab>
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩አምላክ፡ ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መስጥመ፡ አጋንንት፡ ዘዕለተ፡ ሐሙስ፡ አቃቢሁ፡ ሩፋኤል፡ መልአክ፡ ኮከቡኒ፡ አግስትአ፡ ጋኔኑ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/>
                    </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="Friday">
                    <note>Referring to <persName ref="PRS1461Afnin"/> as protector.</note>
                    <ab>
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩አምላክ፡ ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መስጥመ፡ አጋንንት፡ ዘዕለተ፡ ዓርብ፡ አቃቢሁ፡ አፍኒን፡ መልአክ፡ ኮከቡኒ፡ ዘተር፡ ጋኔኑ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/>
                    </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="Sunday1">
                    <note>Referring to <persName ref="PRS8065Raguel"/> as protector.</note>
                    <ab>
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩አምላክ፡ ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መስጥመ፡ አጋንንት፡ ዘዕለተ፡ ቀዳሚት፡ አቃቢሁ፡ ራጉኤል፡ መልአክ፡ ኮከቡኒ፡ ዙኃል፡ ጋኔኑ፡
                        <gap reason="ellipsis"/>
                    </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="Sunday2">
                    <note>Referring to <persName ref="PRS14319Sakuel"/> as protector.</note>
                    <ab>
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩አምላክ፡ ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መስጥመ፡ አጋንንት፡ ዘዕለተ፡ እሑድ፡ አቃቢሁ፡ ሳቁኤል፡ መልአክ፡ ኮከቡኒ፡ ሸመረግ፡ ጋኔኑ፡
                        <gap reason="ellipsis"/>
                    </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
        </body>
